ation over a 30-hour period using a single mapping\nexperience, and allowing experience-based localization to scale to long\ndeployments with dramatically reduced data requirements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Apr 2019 19:38:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 8 Dec 2019 17:06:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 13 Jan 2020 03:53:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2020 20:23:40 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 5 Jul 2022 04:40:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-06"}
