ets. We hope that our open-source platform and these\nfindings will advance research in embodied AI.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2019 03:52:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 25 Nov 2019 01:39:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-26"}
