en the exchange interactions occurring inside each layer\nand across the interface may induce the canted ferromagnetism of Ni$^{2+}$\nions, resulting in weak magnetization in the 1 ML LNO adjacent to the\ninterface.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2019 11:10:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-25"}
